                      </svg>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Photos and logos and GIFs â€” oh my!</h2>
                <p className="text-gray-600 max-w-md mx-auto mb-8">
                  Upload images here so everyone on your team can use them.
